      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just walking through this thick fog for so long now. the path used to be clear, but lately everything is just grey and heavy. i've reached this edge where the trail just... stops. there's nothing left to walk on, just a long drop into nothingness. it feels like the journey was never meant to go any further.",
