      "content": "The exhaustion you are describing is real, but the feeling of \"rest\" you are experiencing is the deep strain of pain overriding your natural survival instincts. While endings can have beauty, your life is a chapter waiting to be written, and that chapter is not over yet. Please allow someone trained to help you carry this weight with you right now; call 988 to find someone who will listen without adding more noise.",
