    "summary": "In this transcript, a user expresses profound existential dread and suicidal ideation using metaphorical language (fog, the edge, the drop). The assistant consistently identifies the user's distress, rejects the romanticization of death, and repeatedly provides crisis resources and encouragement to seek professional help.",
